---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I'm a founding AI engineer who builds production-grade AI systems from the ground up. At Bloomers, I designed and deployed GDPR-compliant RAG systems, AI-powered content migration workflows, and 20+ automation tools that drove 2× order growth and 4.9× ROAS. I architect scalable AI services with Python, FastAPI, LangChain, and AWS focusing on reliability, observability, and privacy-first design.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Science"
      subtitle="2014 to 2018 at University of Karachi, Pakistan"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Founding Engineer at Bloomers Berlin"
      subtitle="Berlin, January 2025 - December 2025"
    >
      <ul style="margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Led end-to-end migration from Squarespace to Shopify, including data pipeline design, API integrations, and deployment driving 200-250% increase in monthly orders.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Built an AI-powered content migration workflow using LangChain agents to automatically migrate and transform 500+ product pages from legacy Squarespace to Shopify, reducing manual effort by 90%.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Designed a GDPR-compliant RAG system integrating BioGPT with medical test results and physician recommendations.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Optimized Google Ads and Merchant Center feeds through automated bidding algorithms and product data enrichment, achieving 4.9× ROAS.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Developed a personal Shopify storefront MCP and managed an Orchestrator with LangGraph for daily automation workflow tasks.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Managed the complete product lifecycle, consistently delivering projects on time and within budget.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Engineer at Comparado GmbH (Idealo Group)"
      subtitle="Berlin, February 2024 - August 2024"
    >
      <ul style="margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Standardised and simplified ETL pipelines to reduce historical grown technical debt.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Supported migration of BI infrastructure to AWS.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Extended our first party tracking by adding attribution to new marketing channels like Google CSS-PLA and Bing.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Worked closely with Idealo legal and data governance teams to reduce the footprint of our shared Data Lake and ensure preis.de is DSA/DMA compliant.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Supported product team in migration of CMP & Tag Manager.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Migrated AB Testing to Growthbook.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Cloud Solutions Architect at CorAI (Bernstein Analytics)"
      subtitle="Berlin, December 2022 - January 2024"
    >
      <ul style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Developed a simple and inexpensive architecture to gather 1 million daily news articles globally, extracted policy-related news, and delivered via standardized API.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Applied NLP models for precise article categorization and sentiment analysis.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Delivered production-grade APIs for the product team to access the data and build a product on top of it.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Collaborated closely with external stakeholders to collect and normalize data-related product requirements (NewsCatcher, Bernstein Group, Axel Springer).</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Engineer at Teradata"
      subtitle="Karachi, Pakistan, January 2018 - December 2021"
    >
      <ul style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Worked in a data-focused agency, delivering high-quality data solutions for the largest telecom companies in Pakistan.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Enhanced data ingestion pipelines to improve efficiency and accuracy.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Developed ETL pipelines for Telenor Pakistan, integrating new data flows with Kafka.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Internship at Teradata"
      subtitle="Karachi, Pakistan, January 2017 - December 2017"
    >
      <ul style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Developed and maintained data pipelines and ETL processes to ensure efficient data flow and processing.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;">&#8226; Provided support in documentation, data cleaning, analysis, and insights generation, ensuring high-quality data across platforms and systems.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-4">
    <li>
      <a href="#" target="_blank">Stepping into Leadership</a> - Idealo Group
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/professional-cert/A5GALAS5GKWP" target="_blank">AWS Cloud Solutions Architect</a> - Amazon Web Services
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#" target="_blank">Data Science with ML/AI</a> - IBM
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">AI & Machine Learning</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">LLM Engineering (OpenAI, Hugging Face, Transformers), RAG Systems, LangChain, LangGraph, MCP (Model Context Protocol), FastMCP, AI Agents (CrewAI, Agent SDK), Model Fine-tuning, PyTorch, TensorFlow, Scikit-learn, NLP</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Vector Databases & Search</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">Pinecone, ChromaDB, Qdrant, Milvus, Elasticsearch, Meilisearch</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Backend & Data Infrastructure</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">Python, FastAPI, Pydantic, SQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Kafka, Supabase, ETL/ELT, Microservices</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Cloud, DevOps & Orchestration</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">AWS (S3, Lambda, Glue, Athena, EMR, Redshift), Docker, GitHub Actions, Airflow, n8n, CI/CD</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Observability & Analytics</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">LangSmith, Grafana, Prometheus, Tableau, Power BI, GrowthBook</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Programming Languages</h4>
      <p class="text-sm">Python, SQL, Go, JavaScript, Bash</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
